snippet.textDisplay:
I think taking a break was much needed for her, because she came back better than ever, instead of going down a dark path, which shows growth and maturity. Celebrity or not, we are humans and no one can truly understand what another person is going through. I used to see her as just another manufactured pop star... But then I decided overlook the superficial aspects and dig deeper. Taylor seems like, at the core, someone down to earth and intelligent. I was watching some of her interviews and she mentions that the best messages are "cryptic" ones. She said she leaves a lot of "Easter Eggs" in her videos. So I found it particularly interesting to watch this video analyzing all of the deeper messages hidden within her upbeat songs: http://greponozy.com/22770479/taylorswifteasteregg



There's lots more out there and it confirms that she is definitely not just a generic pop star...more like a genius one...
